  • Exports

Utilities to check whether a type M verifies the monad laws.

This module is meant to be used in test suites.

Concepts cannot currently be used to implement the monad concept in Nim. See this related issue.

Imports

laws/flatmapper, laws/specs, laws/verdict, laws/flatmapper/constructors
